    • Method Detail

      • onTravelDistance

        void onTravelDistance(Error error,
                      Place from,
                      Place to,
                      int distanceM)
        A callback with the travel distance in meters to the specified location. e.g. "What is the distance between Vancouver and Seattle".
        Parameters:
        error - Error information for calculating travel distance. If Error.FAILED, distance of less than 0 will be returned.
        from - "From" Place. If null, current position is implied
        to - "To" Place.
        distanceM - Distance in meters
